#lakshminakshathraofficialyoutubechannel  #kollamsudhi #lakshminakshtra #kollamsudhifamily

As a skin care enthusiast I have noticed that skin issues vary from age to age. So I have felt the skin care should also  be crafted according to age requirements.  So here we have a complete solution for the most common skin issues according to age. That's Vanaura Organics Rejuvinita Gold Series.
It's best for the night skin treatment, making your skin flawless day by day.

Explore Rejuvinita overnight regenerist gold series 
Why Rejuvunita gold series?

This specially designed overnight regenerist cream, artistically crafted for specific age groups, transforms into a potent blend of natural ceramides, peptides, vitamins, amino acids, fruit actives, flower actives, plant actives, root, and bark actives. It effectively addresses and guards against various skin conditions caused by environmental pollution, climatic disturbances, and age-related damage across diverse age groups.
It enhances natural health glow and Clears blemishes giving a youthful radiance.

snippet.description:

♪ Jio Saavn : https://www.jiosaavn.com/album/kuware-rahab/qR9HIFMiDT0_
♪ Wynk : https://wynk.in/u/lB8D1tkA2
♪ Watch To Earn on FanTV - https://fantv.in/watch/video-neelkamal-singh-shilpi-raj-kuware-rahab-vn4cMI
♪ Apple Music : https://music.apple.com/us/album/kuware-rahab-single/1722927815
♪ Amazon Prime Music : 
♪ YouTube Music : https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=Ms1EsS1D0lQ&si=4ah6c0NhQtX4o-75
♪ Hungama : 
♪ Resso : https://www.resso.com/album/7316642223532148738?

Lyrics - 
लड़का:- धीरे धीरे जान अनजान होत बाड़ू
मरता लईका सेयान होत बाड़ू
बोल सेनुर बनब की सिंगारे रहब
लड़की:- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....

लड़का:- सब मान जाई ना त जान जाई,ए रानी हो जा तू राजी हो
रहबु कुँआरे ना तोहरा दुआरे जानू हमार बाजा बाजी हो
लड़की:- कबो छोड़ब ना वादा ना तोड़ब ए जान तनि हमरा प राख भरोसा
बानी लाइल तू खा ल ना डोसा ए जान मुँह कर ना जइसे समोसा

लड़का:- कर ना हद,बड़ी होता दरद, बोल मरद बनब की ईयारे रहब
लड़की:- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....
पापाजी के भले दुआरे रहब शादी तोसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब


लड़का :- छूटी ना प्यार परिवार भले छूटी,देखब के हमरा के बोली हो
क ल सगाई तबे तोहार आई,नीलकमल घरे डोली हो

लड़की :- काहे मनवा में फूट ता लावा, ई मोहब्बत प बा तोहरे दावा
मिली आशु दिल मे ना में जगह, केहू आई ना तोहरा अलावा
लड़का :- जवने ही रात, कह आई बारात, मयूर बान्हि खड़ा अपना कपारे रहब

लड़की :- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....
पापाजी के भले दुआरे रहब शादी तोसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब

#NewSong #ShilpiRaj #NeelamGiri #bhojpurisong

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3965 | 27 Dec 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3965: Meeting Ka Reason
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal notices Bhide has not arrived at the clubhouse, he inquires Taarak about his whereabouts. Taarak assures Jetha that he is not cognizant of Bhide. The residents of Gokuldham gradually arrive, but Bhide is nowhere to be found. Jetha and the other members are curious about the cause of Bhide's meeting. Finally, Madhavi and Bhide come, but they inform everyone that it was Tapu Sena who asked for the rendezvous.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3964, 26 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Latka Official Video | Zaara Yesmin | Siddharth Nigam | Amit Mishra | Shilpa Surroch |New Hindi Song
snippet.description:
Tips Music Presents Kumar Taurani’s “Latka” Song
Immerse yourself in the soulful vibes of Zaara Yesmin's latest Hindi pop sensation, featuring the dynamic Siddharth Nigam! 🌟Let the enchanting vocals of Amit Mishra and Shilpa Surroch take you on a musical journey in this sneak peek!

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Official, Subscribe on the below link.
http://youtube.com/tipsofficial

Audio Credits:
Singer: Amit Mishra & Shilpa Surroch
Music Composer: The Real Emotions 
Lyricist: Ubaid Taj
Music Programmer: Aakash Rijia
Mix Mastering: Aftab Khan At Headroom Studios
Mix Assistant : Vatsal Chevil
Original Music: A.R. Rahman
Original Singer: Swarnalatha
Original Lyricist: P.K. Mishra

Video Credits:
Directed By: The Real Emotions.
Production Manager: Kishore Hinduja
DOP: Jigar Khan
Steady: Sidesh 
Art Director: Ketki Ghuge 
Assistant Art: Dharmendra Prajapati 
Choreographers: Shyam Yadav & Juhi Arora
Choreography Team : Priyanshu Tyagi ,Sanjana Bamrara, Swapnil Subhash Nagarkar, Alisha Behura

Edit: Nitin Fcp
Asst Editor Saurabh Singh
DI: Bhusan Mathre 
Production & Concept By The Real Emotions Entertainment
Dancers Costume Supervision: Meenal Shah

Zaara Yasmin's Team:
Costume By Luxeboon
Hair & Makeup: Mohammad Ashfaq & Nilofer Khan

Siddharth Nigam’s Team:
Makeup & Hair: Chetan Poojari, Yash & Rakesh
Costume: Mishti Doi
BTS Photography: Sagar Sawarkar

Lyrics:
Nazre Ruke Jo Mujh Pe Ho Jaye Woh Deewana,
Paane Ke Koshish Mei Hai Peeche Saara Zamaana,
Guzroo Yaha Se Jo Main
Ho Jaye Na Hungama…
Aashique Hai Saare Mere Karte Rahe Bahana ….
Chor Denge Chor Denge Hum 
Has Ke Yun Chor Denge Hum…
Dhin Tak Dhin Tak Dhin
Nacha Ke Dikha Denge Hum …

Latka Dikha Diya Humne,
Jhatka Laga Hai Kyu Tumko ?
Tada … O Tumko Tada…. 
Matka Ke Chal Diye Hum Jo 
Khatka Hua Hai Kyu Tum Ko ?
Tada … O Tumko Tada …..

Hey Senorita 
Teri Kitni Kara Main Tareefa ?
Sunn Bonita 
Aise Door Na Ja , Kareeb Aaa…..

Main Toh Deewana Tera,
Sun Le Fasana Mera… 
Tere Liye Maine Chora Hai Sabko
Yun Toh Na Dil Ko Dukha…

Tod Denge Tod Denge Hum, 
Jo Hai Yeh Tere Bharam,
Rule Kare Jag Saara 
Aur Hum Hi Kare Hai Run ….. 

Latka Dikha Diya Tune
Jhatka Laga Hai Yun Dil Ko 
Tada O Tumko Tada…
Matka Ke Chal Diye Tu Jo
Atka Hua Hai Dil Yeh Toh
Tada O Tumko Tada….

Karti Hu Guroor
Tujhko Main Yeh Du Bata…
Deewane Door Ja 
Na Mujhko Tu Yun Sata….

Main Woh Aatish Jo Jala Du ,
Bekhayali Ka Sama Hu…
Jo Na Utre Woh Nasha Hu…
Main Woh Raaj Ek Gehra Hu…..
Jo Mita De Woh Bala Hu .. 
Main Toh Sab Ki Tamanna Hu … 

Teri Neendein Uda Du…..
Teri Shamein Saja Du…..

Latka Dikha Diya Tune
Jhatka Laga Hai Yun Dil Ko 
Tada O Tumko Tada…
Matka Ke Chal Diye Tu Jo
Atka Hua Hai Dil Yeh Toh
Tada O Tumko Tada….

Latka Dikha Diya Humne,
Jhatka Laga Hai Kyu Tumko ?
Tada … O Tumko Tada…. 
Matka Ke Chal Diye Hum Jo 
Khatka Hua Hai Kyu Tum Ko ?
Tada … O Tumko Tada …..

snippet.title: #Video | Jhumka Tutal Ho | Ritesh Pandey | Arohi Bhardwaj | Sapna Chauhan | New Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
अब #WhatJhumka नाही #JhunkaTutalHo गाना  लेकर आयल बाटेन आपके अपने सुपरस्टार  #RiteshPandey #ArohiBhardwaj| 

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:   @SaregamaHumBhojpuri 

Album - Jhumka Tutal Ho
Hindi - झुमका टूटल हो
Singer - Ritesh Pandey And Arohi Bhardwaj
Lyricist – Pawan Pandey 
Additional lyrics - Raja Kesri
Music - Saif Ali (Music Saify)
Feat - Sapna Chauhan 
Mix and Mastered - Aadil Rizvi
Harmonium - Varun Sharma 
Banjo - Pawan Banjo
Arrangement And Programmer - Saif Ali
Director And Choreographer - Lakkie Vishwakarma 
Assistant Choreographer - Ashu And Suresh 
Dop - Yogesh Singh 
Editor - Anand Kumar (Santu)
Di - Rohit Singh 
Production - Amit And Kamlesh

Lyrics:
M:- चलेलु त हुचकी आवे; 
             चेहरा प ना मुस्की बावे
तहरा मे गलती बा की बाटे भतार मे 
काहे तेल छपले बारु अपना कपार मे 
F:- झुमका टूटल हो रात सैया संग तकरार मे -2
लाज के बतिया का हम बताई पूछे ल बेकार मे  झुमका:::::::
                   आंतरा
M:- चिकन चाकन देह तहार भइल बाटे रुखर
रात भर सिटी मारले होकाबु जैसे कुकर
F:-  एकही त हाल बाटे सारा मरद के 
माजा लीहे भले मेहर मरे दरद् से
M:- कमी काउनो होखे नाही देहब् श्रृंगार मे ;  चल जोरवा दीही सोना के बाजार मे 
F:-  झुमका::::::::
                        आंतरा
M:- हुलिया बताव ता हिलावल बारु जोर से 
फुलाल बाटे ठोर रागारायल बाटे ठोर से
F:- माजा मे सजा राते मिल गउवे भारी 
दिया बुता के पिया धउवे अक्वारी 
M:- पवन रितेश के घुमावत रहलू प्यार मे 
बड़ी चोना करत रहलू तु त कुवार मे
F:- झुमका::::::::

snippet.title: Don’t let this happen In your Mid 30’s or 40's & How I Recovered
snippet.description:
I share my personal experience of how I had ignored my health of all these years, just being a workaholic and how in the past 6 months my health took a toll on me and what helped me recover out of this health issue.  

I feel if you are in your mid thirties or forties this video is specially important as we are working professionals due to our work and lifestyle ignore our health, which is one of them most important thing.

snippet.title: Baylagaam Mega Ep 89 - [Eng Sub] Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 27th Dec 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Baylagaam Mega Ep 89 - [Eng Sub] Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 27th Dec 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

Written By: Huma Hina Nafees
Directed By: Zahid Mehmood
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Hi guys, hope you are doing well. 
Looking for ways to flaunt the healthy skin of your dreams this festive season? In today’s video, I’m going to reveal how to achieve spotless, bright skin in three simple steps by using Garnier vitamin C skincare products. So, without further ado, let’s get started. 

Vitamin C, being one of the most effective ingredients in the skincare industry, offers a variety of benefits to the skin. And to make the most of this ingredient, it’s crucial to include it in your skincare routine, be it as a cleanser, serum, moisturiser or more, especially when the festive season is here. So, to help you flaunt spotless, bright skin and prep it for the festive season, here’s a simple yet super effective 3-step skincare regimen to cleanse, treat and seal moisture in your skin effortlessly – 

Step 1: Start by cleansing your face with the Garnier Bright Complete Face Wash to get rid of dirt, dust, oil, sebum, and impurities. Apply the face wash on wet face and massage gently, avoiding the eye contour area. The vitamin C face wash helps reduce dullness and restore your glowing, healthy-looking complexion. It also helps lessen dark spots and acne marks in just a few days, while leaving the skin feel bright. The Garnier Vitamin C face wash is gentle on the skin and suitable for all skin types. 

Step 2: Next, using the dropper take out a pea-sized amount of the Garnier Vitamin C Serum and apply it on cleansed skin. Dab the Garnier face serum all over your face and neck using small, gentle tapping motions. Enriched with 30X vitamin C, the Garnier serum fades dark spots and dull skin in just three days. It is made with a combination of vitamin C, niacinamide and salicylic acid to give your skin an instant boost of freshness and brightness. The lightweight and non-oily formula instantly penetrates the skin and makes it feel super comfortable all day long. The vitamin C face serum is available in four different sizes for you to choose from and is formulated without sulphates and parabens. 

Step 3: Finish off your three-step vitamin C routine by applying the Garnier Bright Complete Serum Cream evenly on your face and neck. The Garnier Serum Cream is made with a two-in-one formulation that helps you achieve the best of both worlds. It easily penetrates the deepest level of the skin and shields it from signs of sun damage such as skin tanning, dark spots, and sunburn. This cream also lightens dark spots, brightens skin, and evens skin tone. 

These products are definitely a game-changer for me. Highly recommended! So, what are you waiting for? Grab your hands on the Garnier vitamin C skincare products right away to #CleanseTreatSeal your skin on the go this festive season. 

I hope you found this video helpful and if you did, don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe to my channel for more such videos. Also, let me know your thoughts in the comments below.  
Thank you for watching, see you soon!

Hi guys, hope you are doing well. 
Looking for ways to flaunt the healthy skin of your dreams this festive season? In today’s video, I’m going to reveal how to achieve spotless, bright skin in three simple steps by using Garnier vitamin C skincare products. So, without further ado, let’s get started. 

Vitamin C, being one of the most effective ingredients in the skincare industry, offers a variety of benefits to the skin. And to make the most of this ingredient, it’s crucial to include it in your skincare routine, be it as a cleanser, serum, moisturiser or more, especially when the festive season is here. So, to help you flaunt spotless, bright skin and prep it for the festive season, here’s a simple yet super effective 3-step skincare regimen to cleanse, treat and seal moisture in your skin effortlessly – 

Step 1: Start by cleansing your face with the Garnier Bright Complete Face Wash to get rid of dirt, dust, oil, sebum, and impurities. Apply the face wash on wet face and massage gently, avoiding the eye contour area. The vitamin C face wash helps reduce dullness and restore your glowing, healthy-looking complexion. It also helps lessen dark spots and acne marks in just a few days, while leaving the skin feel bright. The Garnier Vitamin C face wash is gentle on the skin and suitable for all skin types. 

Step 2: Next, using the dropper take out a pea-sized amount of the Garnier Vitamin C Serum and apply it on cleansed skin. Dab the Garnier face serum all over your face and neck using small, gentle tapping motions. Enriched with 30X vitamin C, the Garnier serum fades dark spots and dull skin in just three days. It is made with a combination of vitamin C, niacinamide and salicylic acid to give your skin an instant boost of freshness and brightness. The lightweight and non-oily formula instantly penetrates the skin and makes it feel super comfortable all day long. The vitamin C face serum is available in four different sizes for you to choose from and is formulated without sulphates and parabens. 

Step 3: Finish off your three-step vitamin C routine by applying the Garnier Bright Complete Serum Cream evenly on your face and neck. The Garnier Serum Cream is made with a two-in-one formulation that helps you achieve the best of both worlds. It easily penetrates the deepest level of the skin and shields it from signs of sun damage such as skin tanning, dark spots, and sunburn. This cream also lightens dark spots, brightens skin, and evens skin tone. 

These products are definitely a game-changer for me. Highly recommended! So, what are you waiting for? Grab your hands on the Garnier vitamin C skincare products right away to #CleanseTreatSeal your skin on the go this festive season. 

I hope you found this video helpful and if you did, don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe to my channel for more such videos. Also, let me know your thoughts in the comments below.  
Thank you for watching, see you soon!

snippet.title: New TOWER TROOP Reveal! (New Update)
snippet.description:
Coming on January 1st! New Card Type! 
Introducing an all new strategy element to Clash Royale!
Change your defence with the first new Tower Troop, The Cannoneer! 
Blast the attacking troops away with Cannoneer's massive cannon! Boom!
More Tower Troops to come soon...

#clashroyale #towertroops #animation #cannoneer 

Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

Episode 3964: Tapu Sena Ka Idea
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu plans a party and explains the plan to Tapu Sena. Bhide declines Tapu's desire to invite everyone to the clubhouse and advises Tapu Sena on what to do for the society's celebration. Goli's push to Bhide spills tea on his kurta as well which makes Bhide furious at them. What will happen in this scenario next? Watch the episode to know more.


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose | From Hitler's Germany to Japan | Full Biography | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Learn about the remarkable journey of Subhas Chandra Bose in this video by Dhruv Rathee. We focus on Bose's daring exploits during World War II as he leveraged the global conflict to aid India's independence movement. His story includes a dramatic escape from British imprisonment, a strategic alliance with Germany, and the formation of the Azad Hind Fauj (Indian National Army). Bose's relentless quest took him to Japan, where he found significant support and established a provisional government. Despite facing challenges, his commitment to India's freedom and religious harmony left an indelible mark on the nation's history. Join us to unravel the legacy of one of India's most iconic freedom fighters, Subhas Chandra Bose.

Bachelor Party releasing on Jan 26th. ಈ ಸಲ ಪಾರ್ಟಿ ಜೋರು!

Bachelor Party, A Paramvah Studios production, starring Diganth Manchale, Yogi, Achyuth Kumar, Balaji Manohar amongst others. The film is created by Abhijit Mahesh & Team, Produced by GS Gupta and Rakshit Shetty. 

Seven years after the comedy blockbuster “Kirik Party,” Paramvah Studios is bringing to you yet another comedy-adventure which will get you high on humour.

snippet.title: Recipe 795;: Thuruvathirai Arudra
snippet.description:
Arudra Darshan is a Tamil festival and this day is dedicated to Lord Shiva. Arudra Nakshatram, which is also known as Thiruvaathirai Nakshatram, during Maargazhi Masam is considered highly auspicious. On this day Arudra Nakshatra also coincides with Pournami.

On this day Nataraj form of Lord Shiva is worshipped during Arunodaya along with holy chanting from Vedas. Being dedicated to Nataraj form of Lord Shiva this day is also considered as the birthday of Lord Shiva. In rest of the India it is Maha Shivaratri which is considered as the birthday of Lord Shiva.

So on this special occasion sending across a video of the recipe that is usually done on Thiruvathirai. 

Kindly have a look at the  Ingredients and recipe ; 

#Ingredients

#Kali

Raw Rice - 1 cup
Moong Dal - 1 tsp
Jaggery - 2 cup
Water - 3 cup
Cardamom Powder - 1/2 tsp
Grated Coconut - 4 to 5 spoon
Ghee - 4 spoon & Cashew Nuts

#7Kaai_Kootu

Ash gourd
Pumpkin
Broad Beans
Carrot
Yam
Raw Banana
Sweet Potato
Toor Dal - 2 tbsp
Oil - 7 spoon
Coriander Seeds - 3 spoon
Gram dal - 3 tsp
Pepepr Seeds - 1/2 tsp
Fenugreek - 1/4 tsp
Dry Chilli - 15 nos
Grated Coconut - 1/2
Curry Leaves
Lima Beans
Asafoetida - 4 piece
Water - 1 cup
Salt - 1 tsp
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 tsp
Curry Leaves
Jaggery small piece
Boiled Toor Dal - 4 tbsp
Mustard Seeds - 1 tsp
Dry Chilli - 3 nos

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 11 Teaser - Har Pal Geo
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 11 Teaser - 23rd December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya
Mehmood Akhtar as Zaawar  
Agha Mustafa as Rayyan  
Hamzah Tariq as Rufi
Ayesha Rajpoot as Shagufta
Mizna Waqas as Husna
Sohail Masood as Mirza Sahab
Birjees Farooqui as Salma

#Khumar
#FerozeKhan
#NeelamMuneer

snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the soul-stirring melodies of "Desh Pehle," a heartfelt tribute to the spirit of patriotism. Song out now on Hitz Music.

Vinod Bhanushali presents, Main ATAL Hoon, starring Pankaj Tripathi, directed by Ravi Jadhav, is written by Rishi Virmani and Ravi Jadhav. A Bhanushali Studios Limited and Legend Studios production, the film is produced by Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh, and Kamlesh Bhanushali.
The film releases on 19th January 2024 in cinemas near you.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3963 | 25 Dec 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3963: Sodhi Aur Roshan Ki Party
--------------------------------------------------------
At the Gokuldham Society, Sodhi and Roshan lavishly celebrate their wedding anniversary. The gathering is enjoyed by all Gokuldham inhabitants, with Tapu Sena receiving credit for the decoration. Later, Jetha is surprised to notice a new visitor reading a newspaper in their dining room. When asked, the elderly guy smiles at Jetha without saying anything. Who is this mysterious visitor?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3963, 25 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1700000084/sodhi-aur-roshan-ki-party-1000257393
